Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}討ち取りし勇者との
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}短い旅の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:45.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}物語は終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者は眠りにつく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:50.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}穏やかな日常を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}この地に残して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時の流れは無情に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}人を忘れさせる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そこに生きた軌跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:01.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}錆び付いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それでも君の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:05.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉も願いも勇気も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:08.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今も確かに私の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}同じ途を選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それだけだったはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつの間にかどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:21.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}頬を伝う涙の理由をもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}知りたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:23.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今更だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:25.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}共に歩んだ旅路を辿れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:29.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そこに君は居なくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと見つけられる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:16.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就像童話故事裡那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}一切迎來結束的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:21.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}從漫長旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}截取出來的一小節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:25.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}很久以前邪惡的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:27.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}籠罩了這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這是與討伐邪惡的勇者的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}短暫旅途的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:45.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}故事結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:50.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}平穩的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留給這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時光流逝如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}帶走人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你刻下的道道軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:01.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也漸漸染上鏽斑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:05.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你說過的話 你的願望和勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:08.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:21.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:23.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:25.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要再次踏上與你走過的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:29.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕你已經不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也一定能夠找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:01.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}おおげさに泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑って欲しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:13.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}鮮明で痛い思い出を抱きしめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:19.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}「さよなら」よりずっと大切な言葉で伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:25.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ありふれて でも特別で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:29.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:37.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかった物が どうして溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう一度　生まれ変わろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:48.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}また私はここを選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:49.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:54.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}あなたとまた巡り合ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:24:00.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう離さない 今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:03.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}約束なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:06.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}孤独に迷う日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:12.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:19.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I'm whispering our lullaby by for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你還好嗎
